Class ClassInjector.UsingUnsafe

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.dynamic.loading.ClassInjector.AbstractBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClassInjector
    Enclosing interface:
    ClassInjector

    @HashCodeAndEqualsPlugin.Enhance
public static class ClassInjector.UsingUnsafe
extends ClassInjector.AbstractBase

    A class injector that uses sun.misc.Unsafe to inject classes.

    Important: This strategy is no longer available after Java 11.
